description:
Today on the show we opened the phone lines to see if our listeners are in a uproar about Elon Musk buying out Twitter like the rest of world. Is it a threat? Moreover,  after Charlamagne gave Donkey of the Day" to a Florida  TSA officer faked burglary report to cover for being late to work, we opened the phone lies to head the craziest lies our listeners have told.
